wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Our website address is: http://51.141.0.77/wordpress.

What personal data we collect and why we collect it

Comments

When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Contact forms

Cookies

If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you have an account and you log in to this site, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Analytics

Who we share your data with

How long we retain your data

If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where we send your data

Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

Your contact information

Additional information

How we protect your data

What data breach procedures we have in place

What third parties we receive data from

What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data

Industry regulatory disclosure requirements

item.content:encoded: The Dell  Inspiron 15 5570 15.6" Laptop is part of our Everyday range of simple and reliable PCs. It's great for studying, working on essays, streaming TV on demand, and browsing the web. Full HD display The Inspiron 15 5570 15.6" Laptop has a Full HD display, letting you watch movies and stream content in brilliant detail. With anti-glare technology, you'll even be able to enjoy your favourite shows in sunlight without affecting your perfect viewing experience. Large internal storage The hard disk drive on the Inspiron 15 5570 has 1 TB of storage space available, so you'll never need to laboriously transfer your important files to another device to free up your hard drive, or make panicky decisions about which album or movie to delete. High quality video conferencing The HD webcam on is perfect for video calling travelling friends, remote family, or for remotely collaborating on a project. Have that long overdue marathon chat free from pixels or lagging, allowing you to catch up free from interruptions. Premium finish Metallic palm rests merge style and comfort for a great portable computing experience. It's also perfectly durable for every day on-the-go use and light enough to take anywhere.

item.title: MacBook Pro 15
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: Touch Bar with Touch ID Apple's Touch Bar replaces the function keys that used to sit at the top of your keyboard, so you can see relevant controls depending on what you're doing. Watching a film? Rewind or skip forward with the Touch Bar. Editing photos? Adjust and crop the image, then select filters – all from the Touch Bar. Touch ID provides advanced and reassuring security to everything you do. Unlock your MacBook securely, use Apple Pay without remembering your password, and access private files with just your fingerprint. Razor thin and feather light The library, the daily commute, an important business meeting – the MacBook Pro 15" is razor thin at 14.9 mm and feather light at just 1.37 kg for brilliant portability. The battery life of up to 10 hours when in use will see you through the working day and beyond. Brilliant Retina display Enjoy enhanced videos, images, and games with the enhanced Retina display that's brighter and more colourful than previous generations. The LED backlit display offers true-to-life images with vivid, realistic details – essential for graphic design, colour grading, and editing. True Tone technology automatically adjusts the images you see to the lighting around you – so everything looks great whether you're finishing an edit late at night or in bright sunlight. Functional features Type comfortably and silently. The keyboard is designed to give you loads of room to gesture and click, and no matter how quickly you're typing out an email, you won't disturb people around you. Tired of figuring out which cable does what? The MacBook Pro has Thunderbolt 3, so you can connect to monitors, charge up your phone, or transfer data from the same port. Easy.

item.content:encoded: The HP OMEN 15.6" Intel® Core™ i5 GTX 1060 Gaming Laptop is part of our Gaming range, which features the most powerful PCs available today. It has superior graphics and processing performance to suit the most demanding gamer. Game for days Featuring the NVIDIA GeForce 1060 graphics, you'll be able to game until your heart's content. From your favourite FPS game to first-person narratives, you can embrace any game genre with great graphics. Gaming has never been easier. It's also compatible with VR so plug in your headset and immerse yourself in the world of virtual reality. Easily upgrade your laptop With a single-panel giving you access to your storage and RAM, you can easily customise your laptop so it's still running as fast as everyone else's for years to come. So you won't have to buy a whole new laptop when new tech comes out. Attractive design The backlit keyboard is specifically zoned so you always know where the most important controls are. And because the backlighting is bright in any setting, even when you're gaming through the night you'll easily hit the right key and destroy your enemy. DTS Headphone X technology You don't want to pay for a great laptop and miss out on audio quality. With DTS Headphone X technology, you'll be able to put on your gaming headset and get true 3D sound. This means detecting your enemies will be easier - you'll know they're coming up on your left and can quickly turn to avoid being caught out.

item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: The Dell XPS 13 13.3" Intel® Core™ i5 Laptop is part of our Premium range, which has the latest tech with high end designs. It's great for editing complex documents, business use, editing photos, and anything else you do throughout the day. Intel® Core™ i5 Get all the power you need for a truly smooth browsing experience with the Dell XPS 13 Laptop. With an 8th gen processor, your laptop can easily take on your everyday tasks, whether they include editing photos, composing presentations or checking out the latest box sets in high definition. 8 GB of RAM means that whatever tasks you need to complete, you can do them all at once without putting a strain on your laptop. InfinityEdge display Let that blockbuster movie take you in even further thanks to the Dell XPS 13 beautiful display. With virtually no border on the screen, the Dell XPS 13 is able to pack more into a smaller frame. With a Full HD display, you can enjoy the latest movies and shows in vividly detailed quality that'll never fail to satisfy. And if you like to work outside in the hot summer months, the super-bright anti-reflective screen means you can enjoy the same level of clarity and viewing comfort outdoors as you can in your office. Movie nights no longer have to be indoors. SSD storage Enjoy quicker start-up times and fast file retrieval, thanks to SSD storage. With no spinning element, SSD is a more reliable storage system. It means you'll only need to wait a few seconds to find and open your biggest files, as well as saving a bundle of time when booting up.

item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: The Razer Blade Stealth 13.3" Intel® Core™ i7 Gaming Laptop is part of our Gaming range, which features the most powerful PCs available today. It has superior graphics and processing performance to suit the most demanding gamer. Powerful 8th gen Intel® Core™ processor Get the power you need to run the games you love without the unnecessary bulkiness. The Razer Blade Stealth Gaming Laptop features an 8th generation Intel® Core™ processor that's more than capable of managing big games like GTA 5 and Gears of War 4. And if you've got a big project to complete, the Razer Blade Stealth Laptop can effortlessly flit between work and play just as efficiently as you. Quad HD screen Don't compromise on quality when gaming or watching your favourite shows on your laptop. The Razer Blade Stealth's Quad HD screen delivers a crystal-clear display that engrosses just as well as your TV. You'll see rich detail in movies and games, in twice the quality as Full HD 1080p. 8 hour battery life Long battery life isn't a feature you'd traditionally associate with gaming laptops. The Razer Blade Stealth 13.3" Gaming Laptop puts an end to that, with a battery that's able to handle 8 hours of game time without needing a charge. This makes your gaming laptop truly portable and means you don't need to scramble for a plug point to avoid letting your team down. Whether you're in a café or on a long train journey, enjoy the best games out there on a device that can effortlessly deal with extended gaming sessions.

item.title: RAZER Blade 15
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: The Razer Blade 15.6" Intel® Core™ i7 GTX 1060 Gaming Laptop is part of our Gaming range, which features the most powerful PCs available today. It has superior graphics and processing performance to suit the most demanding gamer. World's smallest Impressive gaming laptops don't have to be big and bulky. The Razer Blade packs a punch despite being incredibly thin. And how about that edge-to-edge display? It has the slimmest of borders surrounding it, giving the impression of a much larger screen. An aluminium unibody construction means the laptop is both tough and light enough to carry anywhere. Powerful performance Combining an Intel® Core™ i7 processor and 16 GB of RAM, the Blade delivers great performance in all tasks, not just gaming. It makes multitasking easy - even with loads of apps open at the same time you won't notice any slowdown in performance. You can even run complex applications and editing programmes with ease. NVIDIA GTX 1060 graphics Enjoy superb visuals that just pop out thanks to NVIDIA GTX 1060 graphics. The graphics card reduces screen tear and blur to give you sharp-looking images and smoother gameplay. You'll notice it most when playing games with hyper-realistic graphics. The GTX 1060 graphics card even supports virtual reality games. VR gaming is so immersive, you'll literally feel like part of the action. All you need is a compatible VR headset (sold separately) to experience gaming as you've never experienced it before. Super quick 144Hz refresh rate The screen has a quick 144Hz refresh rate, which means gameplay is blur-free. It's ideal for playing racing games and shooters, where the action is frantic. With a fast refresh rate, you won't miss a single detail even when the action heats up during an intense online battle. Vapor Chamber Cooling Worried about your laptop overheating? Don't be. Razer's Vapor Chamber Cooling system spreads heat more evenly to keep the insides as cool as possible. The benefit? Better and more reliable performance on the most power-intensive games and fancy editing applications.

item.title: APPLE MacBook Air 13
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: The MacBook Air is powered by an Intel® Core™ i5 processor that's fast and reliable enough to handle even the most demanding photo and video editing software. Combining impressive Intel® UHD Graphics with a stunning Retina Display screen, everything from blockbuster movies to everyday browsing is a visual joy. And with 8 GB RAM, your MacBook Air can run several applications simultaneously. So, you can get it all done quicker. Solid state storage At the heart of the MacBook Air is a solid state drive with 128 GB of storage space. So, there's plenty of room for your work projects, movies, photos and music. SSD storage gives you lightning fast loading times, so you can get to your files in a flash. Browse all day Forget the mid-day recharge. The MacBook Air with Retina Display will give you up to 12 hours of web browsing, or up to 13 hours of the content you love on iTunes. That's plenty for the entire working day, as well as your entertainment on the journey to and from the office. So, however far away you are from a plug point, you'll never need to worry about staying connected. Unlock your MacBook securely Forgotten passwords are a thing of the past thanks to the MacBook Air's Touch ID sensor. Simply place your finger over the sensor to unlock your MacBook with nothing but your fingerprint, for effortless security wherever you are. It's great for accessing sensitive documents and system settings too, so you can keep everything important safe, without needing a password. And if you love retail therapy, Touch ID makes it even easier to pay. Simply select Apple Pay at the checkout, and with one touch you're done.

  • Intel® Core™ i5 Processor
  • RAM: 8 GB / Storage: 128 GB SSD
  • Retina display
  • Battery life: Up to 13 hours

item.title: APPLE MacBook 12
item.dc:creator: adminteam5
item.content:encoded: At just 13.1 mm thin and weighing under one kg, the Apple MacBook is made for computing on the move. You can slip it into a bag or case and enjoy access to everything that matters without compromising luggage space. A seventh generation Intel Core processor speeds up all your daily tasks, such as opening PDF files and loading videos. Packed full of performance and high-end features including a better-than-HD screen and super-fast SSD storage, the new MacBook is the ultimate Apple laptop for computing on-the-go. Force Touch trackpad The MacBook 12" features Apple's Force Touch trackpad. Rather than a normal ‘click', it vibrates to let you know a click has been registered. You click anywhere on the pad, so you aren't confined to using buttons at the bottom like most trackpads. You get different results depending on how hard you press, so you can activate double and left clicks simply by pressing slightly harder. All the normal Apple gestures are still present, so you can move between software, pages and applications with simple finger movements. 12-hour battery life The 12 hour battery life means you can work all day between charges. If you do need to top up, simply connect a USB-C cable to the MacBook. USB-C is the next-generation of PC connectivity, and allows you to connect monitors, external storage, peripherals, and more. macOS Sierra The Mac Pro runs on Apple's intuitive macOS Sierra operating system. Simple to navigate yet capable of professional-level computing, it provides an expressive platform for you to work and play the way you want. iCloud is integrated into every aspect of macOS Sierra, so you can share documents between all your Apple products and enjoy the peace of mind that comes with automatic backup.

item.content:encoded: The HP Spectre x360 15-ch054na 15.6" 2 in 1 is part of our Premium range, which has the latest tech with high end designs. It's great for editing complex documents, business use, editing photos, and anything else you do throughout the day. Intel® Core™ i7 Processor Work or play, the Spectre x360 15-ch054na won't let you down. It's built for high performance, and bringing your ideas to life. It's all made possible thanks to a powerful Intel® Core™ i7 Processor and 16 GB of RAM that makes light work of complex photo and video editing applications. Programs open faster, and you'll enjoy shorter loading times. A 1 TB solid state drive offers plenty of space to store all your files, music, and movies. So, you can work on your important projects, and still have storage to spare. 4K Ultra HD display With a 15.6” 4K Ultra HD screen, you can enjoy the best picture possible while you're working or when you're on the move. The picture quality is up to four times more detailed than Full HD, so your favourite Netflix movies, and photos will look positively jaw-dropping on it. 2 in 1 Can't decide whether to get a laptop or tablet? The HP Spectre x360 is both. Its 2 in 1 design lets you switch from laptop mode to tablet mode in seconds. Laptop mode is great if you're working or surfing the web at home, and tablet mode is perfect if you want to watch movies on the train. Windows Ink Windows Ink lets you draw and illustrate on your computer screen as if it were an artist's canvas. In the box you'll find a stylus that you can use to design, sketch, and paint. Bring your ideas to life professionally for your creative tasks, or doodle just for fun. You can even use it in tablet mode to jot down notes just like a real notepad.
